{{unsourced|date=May 2017}} {{notability|date=May 2017}} {{Infobox film | name = Curse of the Forty-Niner | image = | caption = | director = [[John Carl Buechler]] | writer = | narrator = | starring = [[Karen Black]] | music = | cinematography = | editing = | distributor = | released = {{Film date|2002}} | runtime = 86 minutes | country = United States | language = English | budget = Unknown | gross = | website = | amg_id = }} '''''Curse of the Forty-Niner''''' is a 2002 horror film directed by [[John Carl Buechler]]. It is known more commonly by its video title, Miner's Massacre.
